{"tid":2437493,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"「連燈力」基金 第六次股東大會 5戰5敗 今周勢必回本全勝!! (開錯台重開)","createTime":"2021-03-08T02:05:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T12:53:45.000Z","uid":149018,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"6bec258053bbe8f07d8b275e3238cd96b6f07930","tid":2437493,"uid":149018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:05:30.000Z","msg":"「連燈力」基金 第五次股東大會操作結算<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Y3hknd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Y3hknd.png&h=112c7849&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xUJJfVy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxUJJfVy.png&h=65ad4d5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n總成本1018.1 HP 剩餘778.25 HP 累計虧損22.18%<br />\n<br />\n「連燈力」基金 第六波操作意見收集<br />\n<br />\n「連燈力」呂布軍成立只為了股東日日有燒賣食，此夢想，不遠矣。<br />\n<br />\n1. 本次操作為ALL IN+餘數制， 收集此帖巴打主流意見<br />\n2. 第六波操作買入主流意見股票後，<br />\n    如餘數過百會由主席選出其中一位巴打之選股<br />\n3. 第六波買入時間預計約為盤前17:00<br />\n4. <span class=\"red\">第六波賣出時間為開市前22:15或盤後08:45由主席決定賣出</span><br />\n5. 本次操作設有+10%止盈及-10%止蝕位<br />\n6. 若結算資金增長5% 隨機向選中買入股票巴打派發Payme燒賣一串<br />\n<br />\n請出招!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4UR2XWx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4UR2XWx.jpg&h=9062ad7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&uarr;由熱心股東提供<br />\n<br />\n第一次股東大會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2430824/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2430824/page/1</a><br />\n第二次股東大會 虧損戰犯 &darr;<br />\n水落石出 #104162<br />\n突然又已一年輕人 #61927<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2431294/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2431294/page/1</a><br />\n第三次股東大會 虧損戰犯=我<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2431887/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2431887/page/1</a><br />\n第四次股東大會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2432849/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2432849/page/1</a><br />\n第五次股東大會 虧損戰犯=世界<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2433746/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2433746/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n本呂布休息過後武力100 智力80操盤，請絕對相信本將軍判斷。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LgnaFrJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLgnaFrJ.jpg&h=e8e7ba7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\">屌，原來開錯台，重新投過啦，智力無減，一時大意。</span>"},{"pid":"9e95fc832a9cae27494f789a94cfb362407f2bfb","tid":2437493,"uid":77039,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:06:03.000Z","msg":"智力-10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05dc1da273eee0a2ad64f592c091aa0fe571d733","tid":2437493,"uid":134094,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:06:08.000Z","msg":"SENS 幫你繼續跌落谷底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7a4b8d2ea6233ee9a93b43bf37d879878ad0a5d","tid":2437493,"uid":149018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9e95fc832a9cae27494f789a94cfb362407f2bfb","tid":2437493,"uid":77039,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:06:03.000Z","msg":"智力-10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:06:41.000Z","msg":"預左你地實笑尻我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f36105f99d3d2536e144279f22da83d057996170","tid":2437493,"uid":160373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:07:17.000Z","msg":"xom"},{"pid":"b80d0234a2a4b70760f4f2927084426b7cf476d5","tid":2437493,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:09:09.000Z","msg":"TQQQ"},{"pid":"8f32fa9fbb255ade329836a15bc28890635201ac","tid":2437493,"uid":311611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:09:42.000Z","msg":"GME"},{"pid":"